<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2023-09-29T10:00:00-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2023-09-29T10:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-29T10:00:00-04:00</updated><title> AMD 首席执行官苏姿丰谈人工智能革命以及与 Nvidia 的竞争</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;AMD 首席执行官苏姿丰 (Lisa Su) 的肖像照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/drebyOuy004eagU0PZ_LdrUdEnA=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72701472/LisaSu_Decoder.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影插图：Alex Parkin / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;在今年的代码大会上，全球最大的计算机芯片公司之一的首席执行官讨论了与 Nvidia 领先的 GPU、AI 监管和技术的竞争。全球供应链。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23894647/amd-ceo-lisa-su-ai-chips-nvidia-supply-chain-interview-decoder &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23894647/amd-ceo-lisa-su-ai-chips-nvidia-supply-chain-interview-decoder" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23894647/amd-ceo-lisa-su-ai-chips-nvidia-supply-chain-interview-decoder</id><author><name>尼莱·帕特尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-09-29T09:34:30-04:00</published><updated> 2023-09-29T09:34:30-04:00</updated><title> Uber、DoorDash 和 Grubhub 未能阻止纽约市送货工人新工资规则</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;纽约送货员&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/U9-HtaKO1sRpBPMScJxSttqEAG4=/0x1:3500x2334/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads /chorus_image/image/72701368/1523375761.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Leonardo Munoz / VIEWpress&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;lwUKld&quot;>;纽约市的送货工人将获得大幅加薪法官驳回了 Uber、DoorDash 和 Grubhub 阻止 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/6/12/23757900/nyc-food-delivery-minimum-wage-uber-eats 的请求-doordash-postmates&quot;>;本市新的最低工资规定&lt;/a>;生效。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;DalPMZ&quot;>;纽约代理最高法院法官 Nicholas Moyne 的裁决将允许 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/9/23/22689396/nyc- Delivery-worker-protection-rules-tips-wage-theft&quot;>;该法律即将生效&lt;/a>;，该法律要求公司向零工工人支付每小时 17.96 美元的最低工资。到 2025 年，工资将升至每小时 20 美元。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;oCF0vJ&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore &quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;外卖工人的反抗&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22667600/delivery-workers- Seamless-uber-relay-new-york-electric-bikes-apps&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;zLYcZq&quot;>;送货工人权益倡导者庆祝这一裁决，并声称这一裁决让他们距离通过工作赚取生活工资“又近了一步”。纽约市拥有全国最大的送货劳动力，由至少 65,000 名无证移民组成，扣除费用后每小时收入不到 8 美元。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;S6vxIb&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;instagram-media&quot; data-instgrm-captioned=&quot;&quot; data-instgrm-permalink=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/CxvrN_Px- ZJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading&quot; data-instgrm-version=&quot;14&quot; style=&quot; 背景:#FFF; 边框:0; 边框半径:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0, 0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); 边距: 1px; 最大宽度:658px; 最小宽度:326px; 填充:0; 宽度:99.375%; 宽度:- webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);&quot;>;&lt;div style=&quot;padding:16px;&quot;>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.instagram.com/p/ CxvrN_Px-ZJ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;amp;utm_campaign=loading&quot; style=&quot; 背景:#FFFFFF; 行高:0; 填充:0 0; 文本对齐: 居中; 文本装饰: 无; 宽度:100%;&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>; &lt;div style=&quot;display: flex; flex-direction: row;align-items: center;&quot;>; &lt;div style=&quot;background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-增长：0；高度：40px；右边距：14px；宽度：40px；&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;div style=&quot;display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center ;&quot;>; &lt;div style=&quot;background-color: #F4F4F4; b